title: Cancer rate for Ground Zero cops 50 percent higher than pre-9/11
text:
Published By: Fox News: Health - Today 
NYPD cops who worked at Ground Zero after 9/11 had 50 percent more cancer diagnoses than officers did in the years before the terror attacks...
